description: Demolition and redevelopment of the site to provide up to 32,192 Sqm of use class C3 (Up to 243 units); Up to 12,700 Sqm of use class C2 (Up to 89 units); up to 430 Sqm of flexible commercial/community use (Use classes A1/A2/A3/A4/D1/B1, hard and soft landscaping works; highway and infrastructure works; engineering works including basement and lower basement excavation works; Plant and equipment and all necessary associated ancillary works.
